n결국 연습은 거의 안 했었지~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":304,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":304,"voiceId":"event183-03-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":304}],"windowDisplayName":"나츠키","body":"이불 깔아놔도 전혀 자려고 하지 않아서\n밖이 밝을 때까지 계속 같이 이야기했어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":304,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":304,"voiceId":"event183-03-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"후후, 그러고 보니 우리도 그런 적 있었지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"ando01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event183-03-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"응. 다 함께 별 보러 갔지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"event183-03-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":304}],"windowDisplayName":"나츠키","body":"연습은 별로 못 했지만\n합숙이 즐거웠다는 추억에서 곡도 나왔으니까\n서로 나름 괜찮았다고 했고","tention":0,"